name: Elena Stewart
description: I find it difficult to boast how good I am, I would rather let you talk to my relatives and friends so they would tell you everything about me: about my good and bad sides, because everybody has flaws. I’m sure, there are spots even on the sun) I would just say that I’m an honest person, faithful and loving wife, caring mother, decent friend. By nature I am a person who loves to learn new things and not afraid of difficulties, the more I try, the less I’m afraid to make a new step into unknown. Now when I’m divorced I take a new step into a new future: to be with the person who loves me, respects my feelings, feels me…that’s why I’m here
